                  <text>Before the Minister gives notice in the <emphasis style="italic">Gazette</emphasis> under subsection (1), the Minister must refer the proposed name to the New Zealand Geographic Board Ngā Pou Taunaha o Aotearoa under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 27(2) or 30</citation></changeable> of the New Zealand Geographic Board (Ngā Pou Taunaha o Aotearoa) Act <changeable>2007</changeable>, as the case may be.</text>
                </para>
